{
  "texts": [
    "There is no doubt that all datasets contain some amount of spam.",
    "However, in the case of Facebook, the presence of spam was apparent from the begining of our analysis.",
    "Consequently, we decided to filter out these spam posts that were hijacking ChatGPT hashtag, which in turn reduced the size of Facebook's dataset to one-fourth (800k to 200k).",
    "This process was based on the simultaneous usage of these hashtags: #reeel, #cr7, #chatgpt, #fyp, #viral (see SI fo further details).",
    "In this section, we outline the key topics identified from our analysis and provide a description for each, highlighting the main discussions shared by users."
  ]
}